About this app

The Oman Foreign Ministry app is the essential travelling companion for Omanis travelling abroad or for visitors to Oman. It helps keep you safe wherever you are and, if you have a problem, it shows you how to get help. It finds your nearest Omani Embassy and gives you key contact information. Lost your passport? Need to contact your country’s embassy in Oman? The app is here to help!

Omanis travelling abroad can register with the local Omani Embassy so they can get in touch with you if there is a problem in the country you are visiting. Available in Arabic and English, the app offers lots of useful help and advice whether you’re an Omani travelling abroad or a visitor to Oman. The App can send you alerts about travel problems and keep you up to date with the latest Foreign Ministry news. You can access the Foreign Ministry’s website and the Ministry’s eServices Portal (in development)
